anchor 6,6
channels X,S,W
palette palette:base
facing mirror-x 1
animations idle=anim:idle
traits Transform,Sprite,DepthSorted
rows
........XX..
......XXSX..
.....XSWSX..
....XSWSX...
...XSWSX....
..XSWSX.....
.XSWSX......
.XSWX.......
XSWSX.......
XSWX........
XSX.........
XX..........
@end

